      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BROOKLYN BRAWL (5) goes very well over this track and trip including three wins. Below best last time at this track (22.56) in a Grade 5, finishing a 4.5 lengths fifth. Rates a leading player. UNPAID DEBT (8) missed the frame latest but had been racing well prior to that including a Grade 5 win two back (19.82) at this track. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. TODOROKI (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Casino behind Line And Sinker (17.05) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Bold showing expected. SANDY BULLET (3) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can atone.",
